{"id": "ChIJlSQsx9iVj4ARB2RczZ7eP8Q", "rating": 4.4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 857, "displayName": {"text": "Din Ding Dumpling House Union City", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Warm restaurant in a strip mall offering Asian noodle bowls, dumplings, and more.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJlSQsx9iVj4ARB2RczZ7eP8Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aS1NVVTNRbXhPUkZoT1ZFVlBkekV0TVV4Tk4zYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Very good soup dumpling restaurant. It can get pretty full, but the line moves fast, and the food comes out extremely quickly.\n\nWe ordered the shredded potato appetizer, cumin dry noodles, braised tendons, spicy wontons, and soup dumplings. The soup dumplings had a lot of soup inside, the shredded potato appetizer was very good, and the braised tendons were perfectly cooked. The spicy wontons were also good, and the sauce was especially delicious.\n\nI would definitely come here again. Service is fast, and the food is worth the wait.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very good soup dumpling restaurant. It can get pretty full, but the line moves fast, and the food comes out extremely quickly.\n\nWe ordered the shredded potato appetizer, cumin dry noodles, braised tendons, spicy wontons, and soup dumplings. The soup dumplings had a lot of soup inside, the shredded potato appetizer was very good, and the braised tendons were perfectly cooked. The spicy wontons were also good, and the sauce was especially delicious.\n\nI would definitely come here again. Service is fast, and the food is worth the wait.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106066383607866198813/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjyLl2oaG0NT-Tj5EMTe-7MDKankwrFQONOmfezIh7d_LPCQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-30T21:01:20.610721324Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aS1NVVTNRbXhPUkZoT1ZFVlBkekV0TVV4Tk4zYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aS1NVVTNRbXhPUkZoT1ZFVlBkekV0TVV4Tk4zYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f95d8c72c2495:0xc43fde9ecd5c6407"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlSQsx9iVj4ARB2RczZ7eP8Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poU1NESlljRTB0UVY5elQxVkljakpKY0RWNU5HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Din Ding Dumpling House in Union City is one of our family favorites! Every dish we ordered was absolutely delicious and full of flavor. The Xiao Long Bao is always a must, and we also love the peach pork, sautéed green beans, Mongolian beef, chicken chow mein, honey walnut shrimp, and hot and sour soup. Everything came out fresh, hot, and perfectly cooked. Great food, generous portions, and a spot we’ll keep coming back to again and again. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Din Ding Dumpling House in Union City is one of our family favorites! Every dish we ordered was absolutely delicious and full of flavor. The Xiao Long Bao is always a must, and we also love the peach pork, sautéed green beans, Mongolian beef, chicken chow mein, honey walnut shrimp, and hot and sour soup. Everything came out fresh, hot, and perfectly cooked. Great food, generous portions, and a spot we’ll keep coming back to again and again. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anna Giovacchini", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115399179732626665134/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwaq9gEkG3qzuk5yULUldq5Dz1DX0tJNYflPMQZ5Fld8PkV3Dz=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-25T03:27:07.420693901Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poU1NESlljRTB0UVY5elQxVkljakpKY0RWNU5HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poU1NESlljRTB0UVY5elQxVkljakpKY0RWNU5HYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f95d8c72c2495:0xc43fde9ecd5c6407"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlSQsx9iVj4ARB2RczZ7eP8Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wa2QyOVdaMFJSV1hrM2NUSjBjVEJoVm1VMGVVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We went here super early around 4 pm and there was no wait. I hear that there’s a bad wait when you go during peak time but we had no issue! The XLB was fire, probably the best I’ve had anywhere in the bay. With some chili sauce was just perf. The spicy wontons were just as good, those were probably my fave and that sauce they put them in is amazing. The zhajiangmian noodles were okay, they were cold which was odd and my friend thought it was probably because they had been sitting out or something. But the flavor was good. The service was fast but our server was not polite. Just business. Overall a good experience though!  My friend and I got these three dishes, we were super full and it was $49 before tip.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We went here super early around 4 pm and there was no wait. I hear that there’s a bad wait when you go during peak time but we had no issue! The XLB was fire, probably the best I’ve had anywhere in the bay. With some chili sauce was just perf. The spicy wontons were just as good, those were probably my fave and that sauce they put them in is amazing. The zhajiangmian noodles were okay, they were cold which was odd and my friend thought it was probably because they had been sitting out or something. But the flavor was good. The service was fast but our server was not polite. Just business. Overall a good experience though!  My friend and I got these three dishes, we were super full and it was $49 before tip.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anna", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104020915299290909111/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXC3suO5ObKiDpxGHJ_qFCd9RZLlHab-uBAl0pvHLLBalkz4JGP=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-23T19:29:02.381389176Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wa2QyOVdaMFJSV1hrM2NUSjBjVEJoVm1VMGVVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wa2QyOVdaMFJSV1hrM2NUSjBjVEJoVm1VMGVVRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f95d8c72c2495:0xc43fde9ecd5c6407"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlSQsx9iVj4ARB2RczZ7eP8Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GbFpWQnhUMWM1VnpOcmFGRkhNVVpNTWxsaldYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Always a line out the door. Come early or order take out (I do this quite often). I haven’t stepped foot into Din Tai Fung since they opened maybe more than a decade ago in the Bay Area, but no regrets when there are Din Dings in the neighborhood.\n\nThe scallop, shrimp and chive pocket is the bomb!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Always a line out the door. Come early or order take out (I do this quite often). I haven’t stepped foot into Din Tai Fung since they opened maybe more than a decade ago in the Bay Area, but no regrets when there are Din Dings in the neighborhood.\n\nThe scallop, shrimp and chive pocket is the bomb!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Allen Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114368795968901780621/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWk54fG2LJS7iD1KLFkc_PYYj3UqHUm1_xtqZS_uLdICw9hMxOxiA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-02T18:42:54.098105009Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GbFpWQnhUMWM1VnpOcmFGRkhNVVpNTWxsaldYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GbFpWQnhUMWM1VnpOcmFGRkhNVVpNTWxsaldYYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f95d8c72c2495:0xc43fde9ecd5c6407"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlSQsx9iVj4ARB2RczZ7eP8Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkUFJXTmtjbmRoY2xFME1XbEZVM1pxUXpKUlUyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Great taiwanse style of food, this is like DTF but a level lower. We came during dinner time\nand it was packed but line moved fast. However, I had to flag the waiter down two times to refill water. I am sure they are short staffed so they need to hire more people to improve the service. Otherwise food is above average and I will come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great taiwanse style of food, this is like DTF but a level lower. We came during dinner time\nand it was packed but line moved fast. However, I had to flag the waiter down two times to refill water. I am sure they are short staffed so they need to hire more people to improve the service. Otherwise food is above average and I will come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kwai Yeung", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102555732917529306558/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsGtoH7DesAsJf8j-hATmWda04foHkJ7Iz8c3RIBNGc4xshA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-18T20:50:43.715137992Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkUFJXTmtjbmRoY2xFME1XbEZVM1pxUXpKUlUyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkUFJXTmtjbmRoY2xFME1XbEZVM1pxUXpKUlUyYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f95d8c72c2495:0xc43fde9ecd5c6407"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJlSQsx9iVj4ARB2RczZ7eP8Q/photos/AWCwydjp5G4VryUJL4Y3tyTBNk3BIvV7PNI5K74E1K9jmligFT436pnrV4NGPZlBRhxhH2uVVHMgXPG-ypHtq8fEjbC0nEJCFYZHcIA3d6_s7AO2Qk